name: Asamiya Athena 麻宮アテナ / The King of Fighters
description:
weight 0.6~0.8 is best.

I created this LoRA in response to a request.

Be sure to refer to the costume prompts in the description.

aa1, purple hair, long hair, hairband, long hair, necklace, bike shorts, earrings, red dress, medium breasts, puffy short sleeves, white sleeves, wristband

aa2, long hair, hairband, school uniform, serafuku, white shirt, blue skirt, ahoge, parted bangs, pleated skirt, midriff, long sleeves, sailor collar



fingerless gloves prompt is your choice.

However, this prompt will not keep your character's fingers in shape with a high probability. This is true for most LoRAs.

The outfit used is the Athena outfit from KOF 98, KOF XIII.
